Method.name: CreationParticipantTest
Method.Implementation:
try{ TSTART
do ##class(Dance.Data.Participant).%KillExtent()
set recorder = ##class(Dance.Data.Recorder).%OpenId(1) set competition = ##class(Dance.Data.Competition).%OpenId(100)
// UDSR -------------------------------------------- set coupleUDSR = ##class(%ZEN.proxyObject).%New() set coupleUDSR.id = 322 set prt = ##class(Dance.Data.ParticipantCoupleUDSR).Create(recorder, competition, coupleUDSR, .st) $$$THROWONERROR(st, st)
// WDSF -------------------------------------------- set coupleWDSF = ##class(%ZEN.proxyObject).%New() set coupleWDSF.id = 125
set coupleWDSF.man = ##class(%ZEN.proxyObject).%New() set coupleWDSF.man.dob = "1980-11-30"
set coupleWDSF.woman = ##class(%ZEN.proxyObject).%New() set coupleWDSF.woman.dob = "1982-03-10"
set coupleWDSF.otherInfo = ##class(%ZEN.proxyObject).%New() set coupleWDSF.otherInfo.city = "New York" set coupleWDSF.otherInfo.club = "Fight club" set coupleWDSF.otherInfo.mainTrainer = "Barak Obama" set coupleWDSF.otherInfo.otherTrainers = "Gordon Freeman, Johnny Cage"
set prt = ##class(Dance.Data.ParticipantCoupleWDSF).Create(recorder, competition, coupleWDSF, .st) $$$THROWONERROR(st, st)
// OTHER ------------------------------------------- set coupleOther = ##class(%ZEN.proxyObject).%New() set coupleOther.key = "KHJGJKGBJFJBGDFDFRRRRRRRFG" set coupleOther.man = ##class(%ZEN.proxyObject).%New() set coupleOther.man.lastName = "Петров" set coupleOther.man.firstName = "Иван" set coupleOther.man.dob = "1990-10-22"
set coupleOther.woman = ##class(%ZEN.proxyObject).%New() set coupleOther.woman.lastName = "Морозова" set coupleOther.woman.firstName = "Виктория" set coupleOther.woman.dob = "1993-05-12"
set coupleOther.otherInfo = ##class(%ZEN.proxyObject).%New() set coupleOther.otherInfo.country = ##class(%ZEN.proxyObject).%New() set coupleOther.otherInfo.country.id = "1" set coupleOther.otherInfo.city = "Воронеж" set coupleOther.otherInfo.club = "Акустика" set coupleOther.otherInfo.mainTrainer = "Аксенов Виталий" set coupleOther.otherInfo.otherTrainers = "Павлюк Валерия, Анищенко Петр" set prt = ##class(Dance.Data.ParticipantCoupleOther).Create(recorder, competition, coupleOther, .st) $$$THROWONERROR(st, st)
TCOMMIT } catch(ex){ TROLLBACK
do $SYSTEM.OBJ.DisplayError(ex.AsStatus()) }
